title: FireBootCamp Gala Day
eventShortDescription: ​​Our graduating FireBootCamp students will unveil the projects they have been working on in the past 9 weeks. You will get to watch the presentations, speak to them in an informal setting, book appointments for interviews, and enjoy a scrumptious morning tea on us.
